text: March 16, 2018 / 3:24 PM / in 32 minutes BRIEF-Freddie Mac Announces Pricing Of $497 Million Multifamily Small Balance Loan Securitization Reuters Staff Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp: * FREDDIE MAC ANNOUNCES PRICING OF $497 MILLION MULTIFAMILY SMALL BALANCE LOAN SECURITIZATION * FREDDIE MAC - EXPECTS TO GUARANTEE ABOUT $497 MILLION IN MULTIFAMILY SB CERTIFICATES, WHICH ARE ANTICIPATED TO SETTLE ON OR ABOUT MARCH 27, 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
